(163, 1, '2023-07-11 06:03:24', '2023-07-11 06:03:24', 'We love multi-purpose kitchen gadgets that make life easier, so that\'s why the Instant Pot (a slow cooker, pressure cooker and stove-top stand-in, all in one) is a go-to for quick meals. Especially this creamy kid-friendly mac and cheese, which cooks up in no time. And after it\'s been gobbled up, you\'ll only have one pot to clean!', 'Ingredient Instant Pot Mac and Cheese', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ingredient-instant-pot-mac-and-cheese', '', '', '2023-07-13 06:45:59', '2023-07-13 06:45:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/recipes/?post_type=foodpost&#038;p=163', 0, 'foodpost', '', 0),
